      "author": "PaolinPaperin",
      "description": "Per-theme flash colours.\n\n- **Box colour** and **bracket text colour** can now be set separately for **light** and **dark** mode under Settings → WikiFlash.\n- The matching pair is chosen automatically from your current theme and updates live when you switch between light and dark — no reload needed.\n- Existing colour settings are migrated automatically (seeded into both light and dark), so your current look is preserved.\n\nOther settings (opacity, duration, corner radius) are unchanged.",
