      "author": "PaolinPaperin",
      "description": "Initial release of WikiFlash.\n\n- Flashes a wikilink's `[[ ]]` brackets the moment you type `[[` and Obsidian auto-adds `]]` — an Xcode-style brace-match cue.\n- Also flashes the brackets when you move the cursor into an existing `[[link]]` (arrow keys or click).\n- Smooth pop-hold-fade; the bracket text fades back to its natural colour with no snap.\n- Fully customizable: box colour, bracket text colour, opacity, duration, corner radius.\n- Respects the system \"Reduce motion\" setting.",
      "downloadCount": 1,
